src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n對沖只係一部份，唔係全部<br />\n佢份對沖合約好似下年定19年到期"},{"pid":"fabf5143ee56d708281a1b4d8eacf69474119214","tid":464252,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T11:26:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新手學野 <br />\n預期油價上升及國泰的燃油對沖持倉，將會對公司業績不利。 <br />\n油升佢d對沖唔係蝕少d咩<br />\n依家升又輸跌又輸？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n升咪輸少啲，跌就輸多啲，結論：都係輸"},{"pid":"8bbc9264f45119d2b411acb97fd0b7938711d0a7","tid":464252,"uid":63934,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T11:32:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家恆指真係得啖笑<br />\n國泰係係香港經濟其中一環嘅龍頭，點會將佢剔出<br />\n一味掉d 爆升股入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又舊又過時既經濟，咪玩啦龍頭，年年都賺少錢跟本唔值留係度</blockquote><br />\ncx 唔係香港航空業龍頭係咩？<br />\n同埋過時？有咩取代左飛機？</blockquote><br />\n航空公司一街都係，業務跟本唔會有咩突破<br />\n國泰本身都唔係咩巨無霸公司，市值低對恆指都影響力唔大，不如加d高增長科技公司仲好，係覺得佢加埋2007有d奇怪下"},{"pid":"4f10c7887a4b98d17c8475a5a552e660f3d2ee96","tid":464252,"uid":61589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T13:50:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>恆指比紅色資本攻佔曬咁滯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以我唔明呢度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 乜撚<br />\n<br />\n十X撤資，因航收皮<br />\n反而香港航空呢d支那垃圾就有得續牌<br />\n<br />\n成個香港跟本已經聞到棺材香<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e2787c94a45ad2eb48a2f0f69cd4131ff4dd3a9","tid":464252,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T14:06:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4b691ef5c7fbba4f28fbfa9bd71857711c749f8a","tid":464252,"uid":57633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T15:23:39.000Z","msg":"道不同不相為謀犯東方雖遠必誅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}